style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">　　（五）母公司与子公司、子公司相互之间发生的其他内部交易对合并利润表的影响应当抵销。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
