</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">母公司在报告期内处置子公司以及业务，应当将该子公司以及业务期初至处置日的收入、费用、利润纳入合并利润表。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
